title: Grateful Dead Live at Town Park on 1987-08-16
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step, Little Red Rooster, Iko Iko, Beer Barrel Polka, Far From Me, West L.A. Fadeaway, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Big Railroad Blues, Promised Land

Set 2

When Push Comes To Shove, Samson & Delilah, He's Gone-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Truckin'-> Black Peter-> Good Lovin', E:Touch Of Gray-> E: Brokedown Palace*

*blown intro, much hilarity, then the whole song. FM Broadcast KOTO.

reviews.review_text:
33 Years ago this Weekend! What an amazing weekend in T Ride w the Boys. A bit shaky at times, but some great music and a killer intimate party!

Brokedown was such a classic moment!
